					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://allthingsliberty.com/2018/05/the-first-countries-to-diplomatically-recognize-the-united-states/#comment-135207"><time datetime="2020-07-05T17:40:36-04:00">July 5, 2020 at 5:40 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Ragusa is Dubrovnik in Latin, and it was independent city-state like Venice. The Republic of Dubrovnik (Ragusa) was officially the first to recognize the USA in the year 1776. That was because they knew the true meaning of freedom (Libertas).</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

