									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>John, thank you for an excellent article! The infant &#8220;diplomatic corps&#8221; of the new United States certainly held their own through some critical years. This reinforces my long-held respect for America&#8217;s founders. It&#8217;s not easy to forge a republic from a monarchy, let alone obtain world-wide diplomatic recognition for it.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-114813' data-commentid="114813" data-postid="16178" data-belowelement="div-comment-114813" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Nancy Maxwell" aria-label='Reply to Nancy Maxwell'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
